attributes.name: max
attributes.description:
Maximum value represented by all progress bars.
Bars will be scaled according to their `data-value` attribute
and this maximum.
Note that, if the sum of all the bars' values are superior to this
`max`

properties.name: max
properties.description:

attributes.name: scale-to-sum
attributes.description:
Scales the bar relatively to the sum of all bars
instead of the maximum bar `data-value`.
